title: Ableton Live Packs
description:
Here i share every Live Packs i ever came across (Ableton User since Live4)

i hope to help everyone who found their version of live here but who'd love to have some more samples and loops and presets and so on to play with.

Most of those packs are downloadable on Ableton.com if you have an account with a licence. but i gess it is not the case for everyone here ;)

Contains puremagnetik retro synth as well

all the packs are up to Live 8 but you can still use them in live 9 so they are still useful especially the session drums multimic and all the goodies from Live 8 suite.

ok i hope you'll enjoy.
